#: casca/help_content.py:31
msgid "Websites, turned into apps. No fuss."
msgstr "Sites virando apps, sem enrolação."

#: casca/help_content.py:33
msgid ""
"Casca turns any address into a GNOME app: icon in the menu, its own window, "
"no leftover browser bar. This guide covers every option on the creation "
"screen."
msgstr ""

#: casca/help_content.py:36
msgid "First app"
msgstr "Primeiro app"

#: casca/help_content.py:37
msgid "Presets"
